00:00:33.260 --> 00:00:34.310
My name is Shelly Lowe.

00:00:34.310 --> 00:00:35.090
I am Navajo.

00:00:35.090 --> 00:00:36.692
I'm from Ganado, Arizona.

00:00:36.692 --> 00:00:39.150
I'm the executive director of
the Harvard University Native

00:00:39.150 --> 00:00:40.640
American Program.

00:00:40.640 --> 00:00:43.710
I want to thank everybody
for joining us this evening.

00:00:43.710 --> 00:00:45.530
I hope that you
enjoyed the film.

00:00:45.530 --> 00:00:48.740
I want to thank Adam Mazo,
who is here with us tonight,

00:00:48.740 --> 00:00:52.850
who essentially made the film
