00:00:58.820 --> 00:01:02.030
who co-produced
the film and served

00:01:02.030 --> 00:01:03.470
as an advisor on the film.

00:01:03.470 --> 00:01:06.830
Professor Duthu is at
Dartmouth University.

00:01:06.830 --> 00:01:10.890
I also want to thank
Tracy Rector who

00:01:10.890 --> 00:01:14.810
created the little postcards
that you have on your chairs.

00:01:14.810 --> 00:01:17.540
This image is of
traditional wetu

00:01:17.540 --> 00:01:20.300
that the Native American
students and alumni

00:01:20.300 --> 00:01:24.020
built in Harvard Yard in 2009.

00:01:24.020 --> 00:01:26.420
And we had these specifically
made for our screening

00:01:26.420 --> 00:01:29.190
tonight here at Harvard.

